@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome

actor "Primary Actor" as PrimaryActor
actor "Secondary Actor" as SecondaryActor

rectangle "System Name" {
  usecase "Create Something" as UC_Create
  usecase "Update Something" as UC_Update
  usecase "Authenticate User" as UC_Auth
}

PrimaryActor --> UC_Create
PrimaryActor --> UC_Update
SecondaryActor --> UC_Update

UC_Create ..> UC_Auth : <<include>>
UC_Update ..> UC_Auth : <<include>>

note bottom of UC_Create
Use case names should be Verb-Noun.
Actors stay outside the system boundary.
end note
@enduml
